        "Fed (raises?|cuts?) (rates?|interest)",
        "(unemployment|jobs) (report|data)",
        "economic (growth|data)"
      ],
      "examples": [
        "Fed raises interest rates by 0.75% to combat inflation",
        "US GDP grows 2.1% in Q2, beating expectations",
        "CPI inflation cools to 3.2%, lowest in two years"
